import React from "react"
import Link from 'next/link'
import { Menu } from 'antd'

const AppLayout = ({ children }) => {

  return (
    <>
      <Menu mode="horizontal">
        <Menu.Item>
          <Link href="/">home</Link>
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item>
          <Link href="/profile">profile</Link>
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item>
          <Link href="/signup">signup</Link>
        </Menu.Item>
      </Menu>
      <>{children}</>
    </>
  )
}
export default AppLayout;
